In the Strength Phase, the focus shifts to increasing strength through lower volume and higher intensity. The workouts include a mix of compound exercises like Clean, Dumbbell Chest Press, and Lat Pulldown, as well as isolation exercises like Mountain Climber and Bicep Curl.

